events.name: Oklahoma Sooners at Alabama Crimson Tide

notes.headline: Capital One Orange Bowl - CFP Semifinal

headlines.description: This season's Alabama juggernaut has yet to be stopped, and Oklahoma's suspect defense sure wasn't going to do it.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 1 Alabama beats No. 4 Oklahoma 45-34 to reach title game

video.headline: Crimson Tide overrun Sooners in Orange Bowl

events.name: Notre Dame Fighting Irish at Clemson Tigers

notes.headline: Goodyear Cotton Bowl Classic - CFP Semifinal

headlines.description: Trevor Lawrence threw for 327 yards and three touchdowns and No. 2 Clemson beat No. 3 Notre Dame 30-3 on Saturday in the Cotton Bowl to reach the College Football Playoff championship game for the third time in four seasons.
headlines.shortLinkText: Lawrence lights up Notre Dame, No. 2 Clemson cruises 30-3

video.headline: Clemson dominates Notre Dame, to advance to CFP title game

headlines.description: Lamical Perine had a 5-yard scoring catch and 53-yard touchdown run to lead No. 10 Florida's strong rushing attack Saturday, helping the Gators cap their comeback season with a 41-15 rout of No. 8 Michigan in the Peach Bowl.
headlines.shortLinkText: Peach Bowl: Gators rout Michigan 41-15 to cap comeback year

video.headline: Florida dominates Michigan behind Franks' big day

events.name: South Carolina Gamecocks at Virginia Cavaliers

headlines.description: Bryce Perkins threw three touchdown passes to Olamide Zaccheaus, Virginia's defense dominated and the Cavaliers beat South Carolina 28-0 in the Belk Bowl on Saturday for their first bowl win since 2005.
headlines.shortLinkText: Perkins, Zaccheaus lead Virginia over South Carolina 28-0

events.name: Arkansas State Red Wolves at Nevada Wolf Pack

headlines.description: Reagan Roberson bulldozed through one tackler and dove into the end zone on an 11-yard catch-and-run in overtime, lifting Nevada over Arkansas State 16-13 in the Arizona Bowl on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Nevada beats Arkansas State 16-13 in OT at Arizona Bowl
